Download vscode and node.js
Terminal commands
npm.init - for json file
npm install -D tailwindcss - for tailwind css
npx tailwindcss init - for tailwind.config.js file
Replace with content: ["./src/**/*.{html,js}"], in tailwind.config.js file in


Make new folder src
Index.html in src also input.css
Type (in input.css)
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

In terminal-   npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch   to specify input and output files and watch to continuously update output

<div class="min-h-screen bg-black"></div>    
This helps class span the entire screen in a responsive way

Link output.css in the index.html in head
<link rel="stylesheet" href="./output.css">

Shortcuts
div*4, tab  to to create multiple(4) divs at the same time
Crl+alt+down key  to edit multiple lines at same time	

